{
  "name": "RPlog_Imperial_Clemency",
  "title": "Imperial Clemency",
  "summary": "Held in the interrogation suite of the Star Destroyer Nemesis, Ambassador Ambrosia, broken by drugs and torture, is visited by the Imperial nobleman Aldus Thel, the Duke of Selene, who dismisses her tormentors and offers a path out of her ordeal. Thel proposes a full pardon, asylum, and a pension if she will sign a confession naming the Rebellion's role in arming Caspar against the Empire, but Ambrosia refuses to endorse what she believes are lies. Thel then plays his cruelest card, revealing that Lieutenant Kovani -- a young naval medic -- is the daughter taken from Ambrosia nineteen years earlier, and threatens to execute the girl unless the ambassador signs. After demanding to see her child in person, Ambrosia presses her thumb to the confession to spare Kovani's life. Thel orders the reunited mother and daughter taken to a shared cell, leaving them the whiskey flask as a parting mercy.",
